            <br />
            <ol>
                <li>Create the DTO's (ResourceModels) for Resources and Categories</li>
                <li>Create the ResourcesController</li>
                <li>Create the controller code for each CRUD functionality</li>
                <li>Generate the view tied to each action (the Model will always refer back to the DTO's we have created)</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
